        "subject": "A quick note on your NogalSolutions inquiry",
        "html": "={{ '<p>Hi ' + $('Call Sub-workflow').first().json.full_name + ',</p><p>Thank you for filling out the form. After reviewing your submission, this isn\\'t the right moment for us to work together — but that can change.</p><p>The most common reason timing is off is that there are foundational things to get right first. I put together a short self-assessment for exactly this situation. It takes about 5 minutes and gives you a clear read on where you stand:</p><p style=\"margin:24px 0\"><a href=\"https://nogalsolutions.tech/resources/automation-readiness-check.pdf\" style=\"display:inline-block;padding:12px 24px;background:#000;color:#fff;text-decoration:none;border-radius:4px;font-weight:bold;\">Run the 5-Minute Automation Readiness Check →</a></p><p>If your situation changes, the form will be here. Resubmissions are welcome — I look at each one fresh.</p><p>Aaron<br>NogalSolutions</p>' }}",
        "additionalOptions": {
          "replyTo": "aaronnogal.va@gmail.com"
        }
      },
